"{\"uid\": \"wtvq.com-special-olympics-summer-games-return-to-eku\", \"entities\": [{\"sentence\": \"Sections  About  Connect With Us  1/0    MADISON COUNTY, Ky. (ABC36 NEWS NOW) -In Madison County, the Special Olympics State Summer Games are returning to Eastern Kentucky University (EKU) in Richmond this week.\", \"from\": 0, \"to\": 211, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 155, \"end\": 182, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Eastern_Kentucky_University\", \"score\": 0.9999999988233412, \"rank\": 1.176570297092949e-09, \"text\": \"Eastern Kentucky University\", \"types\": [\"Q43229\", \"Q3918\", \"Q24229398\", \"Q2385804\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Eastern_Kentucky_University\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Eastern_Kentucky_University\"}, {\"begin\": 184, \"end\": 187, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Eastern_Kentucky_University\", \"score\": 0.9999999999979536, \"rank\": 2.071258070479303e-12, \"text\": \"EKU\", \"types\": [\"Q43229\", \"Q3918\", \"Q24229398\", \"Q2385804\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Eastern_Kentucky_University\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Eastern_Kentucky_University\"}, {\"begin\": 192, \"end\": 200, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Richmond_Football_Club\", \"score\": 0.9985881408181729, \"rank\": 0.0014138553465270634, \"text\": \"Richmond\", \"types\": [\"Q43229\", \"Q24229398\", \"Q12973014\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Richmond_Football_Club\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Richmond_Football_Club\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Organizers expect more than a thousand Special Olympics athletes and over 500 volunteers from across the state to participate.\", \"from\": 212, \"to\": 338, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"The games will take place from Friday through Sunday, with a number of events leading up to them.\", \"from\": 340, \"to\": 437, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Staff and volunteers will begin arriving on campus Wednesday.\", \"